OL,3,C'Crucial' railway line reopens as
OL,4,Csignalling upgrade programme concludes
OL,6,FA rail route connecting England and
OL,7,FScotland has reopened, following the
OL,8,Fconclusion of an overhaul of the
OL,9,Fsignalling system.
OL,11,FThe Carlisle to Lockerbie line and the
OL,12,FCarlisle to Dumfries line had been
OL,13,Fclosed for seven days to facilitate
OL,14,Fthe work, which was completed by
OL,15,FWednesday 7 January.
