OL,3,C'Crucial' railway line reopens as
OL,4,Csignalling upgrade programme concludes
OL,6,FIn addition, CCTV has been upgraded at
OL,7,FFloriston level crossing in
OL,8,FRockcliffe, Cumbria.
OL,10,FChristian Irwin OBE, Network Rail
OL,11,FCapital Delivery director for the
OL,12,FNorth West and Central region, said:
OL,13,F"Today is the start of a new era for
OL,14,Fthe way we signal freight and
OL,15,Fpassenger trains through Carlisle and
OL,16,Fnorth into Scotland.
