OL,3,C'Crucial' railway line reopens as
OL,4,Csignalling upgrade programme concludes
OL,6,FMatt Kent, director of operations and
OL,7,Fmanufacturing, rail infrastructure at
OL,8,FSiemens Mobility UK&I, said: "This
OL,9,Fextensive signalling upgrade includes
OL,10,Fstate-of-the-art digital trackside
OL,11,Fequipment, fully compatible with
OL,12,FEuropean Train Control System (ETCS)
OL,13,Fstandards to enable future
OL,14,Fintegration. These enhancements will
OL,15,Fhelp future-proof the line, delivering
OL,16,Fenhanced reliability and efficiency."
OL,18,FNetwork Rail thanked passengers
OL,19,Fimpacted by the New Year closure for
OL,20,Ftheir patience while the work was
OL,21,Fcompleted.
